      "type": "feature",
      "img": "icons/equipment/head/crown-gold-red.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The Wight-Lord continually emanates supernatural cold. Any creature that ends its turn adjacent to the Wight-Lord takes 2 cold damage.</p>",
          "director": "<p>This passive damage aura punishes melee-heavy parties. Combined with Fellblade's frightened effect, it creates a 'damned if you do, damned if you don't' situation for front-line fighters.</p>"
